<h2 class="auto-style1">'THE NEW ONE MINUTE MANAGER'S GAME PLAN'</h2>
<hr>
<h3 class="auto-style1">START</h3>
<p class="auto-style1">Let people know up front what you are going to do to help them win.</p>
<h2 class="auto-style1">SECRET ONE:  SET ONE MINUTE GOALS</h2>
<p class="auto-style1">Make it clear what the goals are.</p>
<p class="auto-style1">Show what good behavior looks like.</p>
<p class="auto-style1">Put each goal on one page  (only a few paragraphs).</p>
<p class="auto-style1">Quickly review goals frequently (daily).</p>
<p class="auto-style1">Encourage people to notice what they are doing and see if it matches their goals.</p>
<p class="auto-style1">If not urge them to change what they are doing and when.</p>
<h3 class="auto-style1">IF THE GOALS OR ANY PART OF THE GOALS ARE ACHIEVED YOU WIN</h3>
<h2 class="auto-style1">SECRET TWO:  GIVE ONE MINUTE PRAISINGS</h2>
<p class="auto-style1">Catch people doing things right.</p>
<p class="auto-style1">Praise the behavior.</p>
<p class="auto-style1">Do it soon.</p>
<p class="auto-style1">Be specific.</p>
<p class="auto-style1">Say how good you feel about it.</p>
<p class="auto-style1"> Pause... to let people feel good too.</p>
<p class="auto-style1">Encourage them to keep up the good work.</p>
<p class="auto-style1">Proceed with more success.</p>
<h3 class="auto-style1">HOWEVER IF GOALS ARE NOT ACHIEVED YOU LOSE</h3>
<h2 class="auto-style1">SECRET THREE: TO HELP TO WIN GIVE ONE MINUTE REDIRECTS</h2>
<p class="auto-style1">Clarify and agree on goals.</p>
<p class="auto-style1">Clarify what happened.</p>
<p class="auto-style1">Describe the mistake soon.</p>
<p class="auto-style1">Say how concerned you feel.</p>
